# Media drop folder

Drop:
- hero-loop.mp4      → Screen 1 background (8s loop, 9:16, MP4 h.264)
- cards/card-1.png   → Screen 8 first prescription illustration (optional)
- cards/card-2.png   → Screen 8 second prescription illustration (optional)
- cards/card-3.png   → Screen 8 third prescription illustration (optional)

App renders tasteful gradient fallbacks when these are missing.
